      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "User exposed easily triggered crasher,  should probably block v0.18. :(    Esp if users trigger this during/shortly after IBD they'll likely corrupt their blockchain state and end up with a days long resync or reindex.\r\n\r\nWe might want to consider reverting #14941  just in 0.18.0, in part because there might be other similar interactions?  (also because we're awfully close to 0.18 to engage in non-trivial fixes)",
